flowchart TD
  A[Sell reman part] --> B[Invoice includes core deposit line]
  B --> C[CoreLedgerEvent CUSTOMER CORE_CHARGED]
  C --> D[Customer returns core]
  D --> E[CoreLedgerEvent CUSTOMER CORE_RETURNED]
  E --> F[CreditMemo issued]
  F --> G[CoreLedgerEvent CUSTOMER CORE_CREDIT_ISSUED]
  H[Vendor bill includes core] --> I[CoreLedgerEvent VENDOR CORE_CHARGED]
  I --> J[Ship core return to vendor]
  J --> K[CoreLedgerEvent VENDOR CORE_RETURNED]
  K --> L[VendorCredit issued]
  L --> M[CoreLedgerEvent VENDOR CORE_CREDIT_ISSUED]
